specs 1


owner should be able to :
    add employee
    fire employee
    edit employee
    make a menu
    edit a menu
    delete a menu
    create a menu item
    cancel an item
    edit an item
    login
    logout
    view past orders for a customer
    view a customer's past order
    view reservations
    view a reservations
    cancel a reservations
    edit a reservations
    change password
    edit profile
    view profile


waiters should be able:
    login
    log out
    view menu
    view reservations
    edit reservation
    cancel reservations
    view orders
    view a customer's order
    edit order
    cancel order
    view profile
    edit profile
    view a customer's past order
    reset passsword


chefs should be able to:
    login
    logout
    view menu
    edit menu
    cancel menu
    add menu item
    cancel menu item
    edit menu item
    view profile
    edit profile
    view orders
    view reservations
    reset password



customers should be able to:
    login
    logout
    signup
    make reservation
    cancel reservation
    edit reservation
    optional to be able to pick appetizers and drinks for reservation
    make order
    edit order
    cancel order
    view profile
    edit profile
    view reservation
    view order
    view past orders
    view past reservations 
    reset password